EmailTemplate.description: Request BM for IBAN implementation in IBAN
EmailTemplate.name: ***JO - request BM
EmailTemplate.subject: Ref nr {!Case.CaseNumber} - {!Case.Subject}
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear Sir/Madam,
Earlier this month we have communicated your representative in Jordan the need to provide us with new banking mandates due to the implementation of IBAN in Jordan (copy attached). Unfortunately we have not received the new bank mandate for your company and this could result in delays in the settlement of your next BSP and/or CASS receivables. Without the IBAN numbers IATA will not be able to process your settlement for BSP and/or CASS.
Should you require any additional information please do not hesitate to contact us through our customer portal www.iata.org/cs
Yours Sincerely,
{!Case.OwnerFullName}
Global Airline Participation Team
Financial and Distribution Services
International Air Transport Association
33, Route de l'Aroport
1215 Geneva 15 Airport
Switzerland
